      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p data-end=\"204\" data-start=\"66\">We are currently experiencing issues with our data pipeline, resulting in intermittent data ingestion failures in the following regions:</p>\n\n<ul data-end=\"281\" data-start=\"206\">\n\t<li data-end=\"227\" data-start=\"206\">São Paulo, Brazil</li>\n\t<li data-end=\"247\" data-start=\"228\">London, England</li>\n\t<li data-end=\"263\" data-start=\"248\">Oregon, USA</li>\n\t<li data-end=\"281\" data-start=\"264\">Mumbai, India</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p data-end=\"528\" data-start=\"283\">The affected data range spans from <strong data-end=\"351\" data-start=\"318\">February 6th to February 13th</strong>. While not all projects were consistently impacted, this timeframe represents the full duration in which ingestion inconsistencies were observed.</p>\n\n<p data-end=\"762\" data-start=\"530\">During this period, data ingestion was unreliable; however, <strong data-end=\"615\" data-start=\"590\">no data has been lost</strong>, as we have backups available for reprocessing. We are actively working on resolving the issue and restoring the affected data from our backups.</p>\n\n<p data-end=\"941\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-start=\"764\">We expect this to be fully resolved within the next week and will provide another update once the restoration process is complete. Thank you for your patience and understanding.</p>"
      },
